    <string name="auto_start_instruction">
    <![CDATA[
    <b>Background Location Access Required</b><br/><br/>


    To ensure accurate <b>background location tracking</b> after check-in,
    please complete the steps below:<br/><br/>

    <b>1. Battery Usage</b><br/>
    Set battery usage to:<br/>
    • <b>Unrestricted</b><br/>
    • <b>Allow background activity</b><br/>
    • <b>No restrictions</b><br/><br/>

    <i>This is required to keep location tracking active in the background.</i><br/><br/>

    <b>2. Enable Auto-start</b><br/>
    Steps:<br/>
    Settings → Apps → Auto-start/Background autostart → <b>Delta iAttendance</b> → Allow<br/><br/>

    <b>3. Disable “Pause app activity if unused”</b><br/>
    Make sure this option is <b>OFF</b>.<br/><br/>

    <b>4. Location Permission</b><br/>
    Set location permission to:<br/>
    <b>Allow all the time</b><br/><br/>

    <i>This ensures location is tracked after check-in even when the app is closed.</i><br/><br/>

    <b>Important:</b><br/>
    After completing all steps, please <b>reopen the Delta iAttendance application</b>.
    ]]>
</string>
